{"tid":88683,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"十日北海道獨遊","createTime":"2017-01-20T18:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T05:39:42.000Z","uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52308477c7857282b7f0126261317cbb4bad42b7","tid":88683,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"首先同Whom*may*care，黨指揮娼，士多啤梨蘋果橙，人黎捉住佢。前個星期起連登問過行程，好多謝你地比既意見。但我最後冇咩點聽到，只有少少修改。因為某啲位上網睇過唔算係自己想去既地方。所以只係修改左個行程，令佢行得順滑啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次係細佬第一次睇雪，去北海道，獨遊。開呢個post 都係想有人陪下感覺上冇咁悶。呢次旅程未必事事順利同有最好既plan，但求安安全全咁過同唔好遲到（平時好準時，預時間好準，但一去旅行就錯晒）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次呢個行程主要想學識滑雪，而滑雪場主要係起啲札幌附近。因為上背包客棧睇過有啲台仔長期起果度，所以聯絡左佢地睇下會唔會一齊玩下。其他日子會去登別，旭川同層雲峽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n21中午到札幌-午夜登別<br />\n22早午登別-夜札幌<br />\n23札幌滑雪<br />\n24札幌滑雪<br />\n25早午小樽-夜旭川<br />\n26早旭川-午夜層雲峽<br />\n27早層雲峽-午旭川-夜札幌<br />\n28札幌滑雪<br />\n29札幌滑雪<br />\n30早午札幌-1615飛<br />\n<br />\n因為聽講北海道好早天黑，所以行程盡早起身同埋預夜晚先坐長途車，希望我估計冇錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇，打打下已經要上機喇。聽日見喇各位巴絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b09daf18d12effeef7f2c81c14ea6c53b15ce7","tid":88683,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:50:18.000Z","msg":"幫我買柒頭T得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ac933898a44d200e423f01da1c019e6e501b19","tid":88683,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫我買柒頭T得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知係邊度買，件tee好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f00f1512e758b68e20875041d4a03fed246e31","tid":88683,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"18個鐘都冇人影？"},{"pid":"ee38515472255fc01775c49af06a4dcdb387efec","tid":88683,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"3a8dd95b50c64c850707bf8519505fcfe82cab51","tid":88683,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"屌你係咁滑雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8044c3d6813e381dec46cc558a1dbf520a82b31","tid":88683,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"相呢？"}]}